表達訴求，仍致力確保珍貴物品不受破壞，亦無意圖搶掠物資。 示威人士對守護香港是真心的。<br />\n<br />\n6. 示威人士會根據現行機制，檢討是次行動是否有不恰當的地方。 受是次行動影響的人士，可透過現行機制作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n7. 未來三年，示威人士仍然有很多訴求需要表達， 希望廣大市民給予機會，讓示威人士更好地表達訴求。"},{"pid":"686a2e1d004eb7eca43d5721c0b7ea919ab06e0e","tid":1275061,"uid":38164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tD3fprXSKOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtD3fprXSKOE&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=089e150e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tD3fprXSKOE</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片係好撚嚴重既指控，已經瘋傳藍絲、廢老、中立派。"},{"pid":"811eb1a2994d9bc6a6a59b205ecfb5613770414c","tid":1275061,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:44:59.000Z","msg":"7.1有女仔掟稀釋通渠水失手，警察立刻急救!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275060\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275060</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家快參下"},{"pid":"5bb0303220f954203bc95b4043163cec3c692468","tid":1275061,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:47:52.000Z","msg":"見到就幫手檢舉 再留言 多一個人嘅力量都好重要"},{"pid":"85cb8efac7668e959bfa81a375f229634e1dfdbc","tid":1275061,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904f20e3ce93f0bce7d431a375c2d827814a9176","tid":1275061,"uid":53922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:37:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣組 之後幾日準備猛烈輿論戰，大家要READY</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeff68b168fc804a13bcb5ec963a832fb3e81eb","tid":1275061,"uid":271431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:52:28.000Z","msg":"可唔可以將立場訪問妹妹個段 翻譯成其其他語言 要加解說"},{"pid":"801ac59d66d2a0547874c79e729386b5faaf594b","tid":1275061,"uid":248470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:54:03.000Z","msg":"d人佔領立法會 林鄭都依然冷漠拒絕對話 係唔係想攪